I guess this is not in the scope of this ticket but I am unsure why we use a Map<string,number> here and export the keys in this complicated fashion.  Would something like
interface CourseScores { absoluteScore: number; relativeScore: number; } 
not be much cleaner and more in the spirit of typescript?

